Packet Tracer - Server Configuration

Objectives

Configure the Ip addressing based on the table
Configure DNS, Web Server and DHCP servers
Verify connectivity and troubleshoot any issues.
Scenario
Your network manager is impressed with your performance in your job as a LAN technician. he would like you to demonstrate your ability to Confirm that all devices are properly configured and troubleshoot any issue. Your tasks include verify all network devices have the basic configurations. configure a DHCP server to provide IP address dynamically, setting our own DNS server for our Web server

In this activity you will configure the YT-R-01 router, YT-SW-01 switch, DHCP, DNS, Web Server

Note: Packet Tracer will not score some configured values, however these values are required to accomplish full connectivity in the network.

